snippet.title: Guilty Gear 20th Anniversary Edition - Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
The original Guilty Gear and GUILTY GEAR XX ΛCORE PLUS R reunite to celebrate 20 years of 2D anime action!

Guilty Gear 20th Anniversary Pack will include:
- a personal letter from Guilty Gear creator Daisuke Ishiwatari
- an artbook with unreleased works of his

Both games included in the pack will be available as separate digital versions on Nintendo Switch, and the original Guilty Gear for PlayStation 4, also releasing on May 17th.

Order Now from:
http://pqube.co.uk/guilty-gear-anniversary/

Come chat to us on our PQube Discord server! 
https://discord.gg/xHS7MnU

#GuiltyGear20th
